{
  "stem": "7160.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was 15, 16 years old, you know, and weak.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Maybe I weighed by that time, about 75, 80 pounds, you know?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He kicked me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I couldn't even get up from the floor after he finished beating me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then I tell him, Albert, I said, God willing, if I get out of here, one day I gonna get even with you.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So-- and then-- and then that-- I forgot something to say.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When-- when we went in the camp over there, a lot of senior people, you know, in their 30s, 40s, you know, they find out their wive and the kids-- the kids they-- they got-- they got killed and everything else.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They say, it's no-- what's the use living?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I go and throw myself in the wires-- on the electric wires, and burn myself-- electrocute.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There's no use living with that kind of life.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- I-- I went, and I tell them, listen.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I say, you have to try to survive just to pay back to the Germans.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Don't give up.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Try to fight and-- to stay alive.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "One day, God willing, we get out of here, and we're going to get even with those Germans.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There's something we're going to do to repay them back.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Don't give up.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There are some-- some did listen to me, some they didn't.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "A matter of fact, I meet two or three guys after the war that said thanks for you.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I-- I am alive today, because I was ready to give up.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So coming back to the place in Warsaw, the-- from there, we walked to-- to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a very short time-- place from Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We spent a couple nights in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
